reviewText: A profound and  radiant description of communicating with our souls through the Akashic Records! There is much to be learned from it. Dahna Fox  has invested in it her very soul and inspiration!
No it was a waste of time and money the material was poor and so was the presenter pass this one up not worth save your money for good material
